{"tid":1901630,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"吳文遠透過傳媒披露馮程淑儀遭廉署立案調查 法院拒受理上訴 即時入獄","createTime":"2020-02-28T02:23:05.000Z","updateTime":"2020-02-28T04:15:40.000Z","uid":22556,"like":2,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"22559aba27b98ae5823fb577831bde8e546aee08","tid":1901630,"uid":22556,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-28T02:23:05.000Z","msg":"社民連主席吳文遠4年前透過傳媒及社交媒體，披露民政事務局時任常任秘書長馮程淑儀遭廉署立案調查，前年被裁定3項披露受調查人身份罪成，判囚4個月。高等法院去年駁回其上訴，吳及後向終審法院申請上訴許可兼保釋，惟終院今拒絕受理其上訴，吳須即時服刑。<br />\n<br />\n吳文遠在被裁定罪成後曾服刑一段時間，及後獲准保釋等候上訴，現時剩餘約31天刑期未服完。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://s.nextmedia.com/realtime/a.php?i=20200228&amp;s=6996647&amp;a=60651811\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fs.nextmedia.com%2Frealtime%2Fa.php%3Fi%3D20200228%26s%3D6996647%26a%3D60651811&d=d7tjXuyQMlDyBW65i2Gj0VT2VSzVBU3ss%2BeERvjOeOk%3D&h=eb7f82e3\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fs.nextmedia.com%2Frealtime%2Fa.php%3Fi%3D20200228%26s%3D6996647%26a%3D60651811&h=4d266a16\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://s.nextmedia.com/realtime/a.php?i=20200228&amp;s=6996647&amp;a=60651811</a>"},{"pid":"e6bf964ed89e4ad617c6f043c6e1d30918f2ca08","tid":1901630,"uid":130898,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-28T02:24:12.000Z","msg":"文遠大將軍坐多排先"},{"pid":"0cd5399721bb3f11b90c07305b7150dbab947fad","tid":1901630,"uid":33028,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-28T04:15:40.000Z","msg":"冇得參選<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}